      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="p:14;61:10">This folder houses custom index definition files that override the standard ones in
