      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="title:4;77:14">Variable overrides: the <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="filepath:25;77:48">common/vars</filepath> folder</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="p:18;78:10">This folder houses custom variable definitions that override the standard ones in
          <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="filepath:26;79:21">org.dita.pdf2/cfg/common/vars</filepath>. As with index configuration, Each file contains data for a
        single language, and should take that language’s ISO 639-1 language designator as its name.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="p:19;81:10">Variable files contain a set of <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/pdf-plugin-structure.dita" xtrc="xmlelement:7;81:54">variable</xmlelement> elements, identified by their
